name: SEER Primary Tumor Behavior Table
title: Breast Summary Stage - SEER Primary Tumor Behavior Table
notes: **Note:** For SEER Primary Tumor codes 050 and 070 ONLY, Summary Stage 2000 are assigned based on the value of Behavior Code ICD-0-3, as shown in this table.
rows: Behavior code of 0 should not be used with CS Extension code 050 or 070.
Behavior code of 1 should not be used with CS Extension code 050 or 070.
All other combinations of Extension and Behavior have Summary Stage calculated by the standard table.
